{
  "stem": "27351.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish profiteers who took advantage of the shortages, food shortages, who made their dirty business with Germans, with Poles, Polish scum of the Polish society.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, oh, they-- they had champagne and dances and balls and food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was so young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what I made out of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's very hard, you know, for me to-- to go back and to think what I as a 13-- maybe-- year-old child looked at.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- I know that I was terribly disturbed by the-- by the children by the sight and the sound of these children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember once I-- I was asked to babysit a little girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her mother had to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was a friend of my mother, whoever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was there along with the child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a little skeleton beggar in rags came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a piece of bread in the basket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And without any thought or hesitation, I just gave this child this bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It turned out when this lady came back, the mother of the child, that this was the only food she had for the entire day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well we had to eat something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my mother, again, performed, you know, little miracles trying to feed me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We used to go for a while to the Jewish writer's union.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was at that time on street that was called Karmelitska.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This Karmelitska was a very narrow street and very, very crowded always.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Of course, it was crowded with people going after their business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was crowded with beggars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And at that time, they started snatching whatever you had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If there was a little package in your hands, they would snatch it looking for food.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
